<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Kant-KdrV-1781.png" class="image" title="Title page of the 1781 edition."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Kant-KdrV-1781.png/180px-Kant-KdrV-1781.png" width="180" height="281" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Kant-KdrV-1781.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Title page of the 1781 edition.</div>
</div>
