<ul>
<li><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=l10VAAAAYAAJ&amp;printsec=titlepage&amp;source=gbs_summary_r&amp;cad=0" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=l10VAAAAYAAJ&amp;printsec=titlepage&amp;source=gbs_summary_r&amp;cad=0" rel="nofollow">Francis Haywood (1838)</a> (First English translation)</li>
<li>J.M.D. Meiklejohn (1855)</li>
<li><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=yW6VR__RAW4C&amp;printsec=titlepage&amp;source=gbs_summary_r&amp;cad=0" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=yW6VR__RAW4C&amp;printsec=titlepage&amp;source=gbs_summary_r&amp;cad=0" rel="nofollow">Friedrich Max Müller (1881)</a></li>
