<li>Rotenstreich, N., EXPERIENCE AND ITS SYSTEMATIZATION: STUDIES IN KANT (1965)</li>
<li>Schwyzer, H., UNITY OF UNDERSTANDING: A STUDY OF KANTIAN PROBLEMS (1990)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/T._K._Seung" title="T. K. Seung">Seung, T. K</a>, KANT'S TRANSCENDENTAL LOGIC (1969)</li>
